data.title: Welcome to Omnipod Bay! - Omnipod on Animal Crossing
data.text:
Don’t just lounge on the beach all day, go on a hunt for a special prize. Hidden within the Podder® Lounge, Gym, and Medical Center are code fragments. These codes can be combined and entered into your island design kiosk for a secret design.

Tip: Use all your camera angles to scope out the needed codes.

The island is full of adventure and challenges. If you get stuck, you can always check the bulletin board. And remember, sometimes what you're looking for may be hidden. Use all camera angles to fully explore the island and find the supplies you need.

A short-sleeve, zip-up jersey that allows your Pod to peek through, paired with coordinating athletic shorts. Wear it while cycling around the island or when participating in one of the many activities at the diabetes camp.

Design Codes

A cheery striped tee and loose linen overshirt, paired with a fashionable white pack full of all the diabetes supplies you need. Explore the island—don’t forget to stop by and rub the belly of one of the cute diabetes alert dogs.

Design Code

MO-YQ09-DNKV-S8WP

The perfect pair of striped swim trunks that hit right above the knee and start right below your diabetes technology. With a Pod on your side, you can relax on a hammock or watch the waves crash at the A1-Sea.

Advocacy Partner

Beyond Type 1 is a nonprofit organization changing what it means to live with diabetes. Through peer support programs, global campaigns, and digital platforms, Beyond Type 1 is uniting the global diabetes community, empowering people to both live well today and support a better tomorrow.

Shirt Design Code

MO-8X2P-5J82-LJ5G

Cap Design Code

MO-BQSG-NKWK-BF97

Traveling to Omnipod Bay is like a dream, seriously you have to dream. Lie down in your bed and select “I want to get some sleep” when given the choice. Then enter the code DA‑9645‑5879‑6910.

Having trouble dreaming? Make sure you have a Nintendo® Online account, check for a message from Luna and make sure “dreaming” is unlocked in your settings. Please note you will need a Nintendo Switch and Animal Crossing: New Horizons® game.
